        <section class="subject-introduction">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-12">
                        <h1>Why study Accounting and Finance in Manchester?</h1>
<p>Manchester is one of the biggest economic hubs in the UK outside of London, with a number of international financial services based there including Barclays, Deloitte, KPMG, AJ Bell and RSM. Manchester's Spinningfields area is the main hub for financial services and banking in the city and with more than 45,000 employed in the financial services industry here, it's a growing centre for international finance.</p>
<ul>
<li>Top NCUK universities in Finance include:  The University of Leeds, University of Birmingham, University of Sheffield and The University of Manchester.</li>
<li>Choose from a range of degree subjects including: Accounting and Finance, Economics, Banking and Financial Management.</li>
</ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-12">
                        
<div class="promotion-banner image-only">
    <img class="mw-100" alt="96% course completion rate for students at INTO Manchester (INTO 2018/19 cohort)" src="https://ctfimages.intoglobal.com/xw2h6mjophtz/4J2Y6lHs0n6w5YkOmkwNC6/e9dbdad4f4a41492ab19d9f2915679f8/MAN_Finance_USP.svg?fit=fill&w=300&h=300&q=80" />
</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
